OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey start towards the east,
OL,6,Fotherwise another sunny and hot day
OL,7,Facross the region. Dry for most
OL,8,Falthough a few showers possible across
OL,9,Fthe Isles of Scilly. Breezy inland
OL,10,Fwith strong winds over the hills and
OL,11,Fnear southern coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRemaining dry and clear
OL,14,Fovernight with the strong winds
OL,15,Fcontinuing along the south coast.
OL,16,FStaying warm inland leading to an
OL,17,Funcomfortable night for some.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
