OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FStaying largely dry and sunny
OL,6,Fon Monday, although a small chance of
OL,7,Fa few showers developing later in the
OL,8,Fday. Remaining windy near the south
OL,9,Fcoast but very warm inland.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FThe
OL,12,Fheatwave continuing into the middle of
OL,13,Fthe week, although there will be an
OL,14,Fincreasing risk of showers and
OL,15,Fthunderstorms, especially by Thursday.
OL,16,FWinds gradually easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
